 Life walked down the hallway. As the sharp pain entered his head he cried 
out in pain. He stuggled to hold it put his strength was no match for the 
dark being. As fell to the ground screaming. He laided motionless for a 
moment. Then he slid up right...his eyes glowed and furious red. He said in a 
cold voice for anyone who may come to the alarm of his screaming.."Just a 
memory clitch..nothing more." He walked swiftly down the hallway and a smirk 
formed on his face.
